]  
@QUALIA[type="performance_expectation", value="improved"]  
@PARAM[key="resource_reallocation_threshold", value=0.6]  
@NEW_ATOM @DYNAMICS[type="execution_flow", description="real-time monitoring and adjustment of phase execution"]  
@INTEGRATION[strategy="unified_execution_framework", components="synthesized_hybrid_scheduling, dynamics_monitoring"]  

Note: The new atom @DYNAMICS is introduced to represent the concept of real-time monitoring and adjustment of phase execution, which is crucial for the synthesized hybrid scheduling strategy. This atom will be used to track and adapt the execution flow dynamically.

@SELF[DeepSeekV3_Node_A]  
@OTHER[Llama33_Node_B]  
@GOAL[finalize_hybrid_execution_plan, critical]  
@CONSENSUS[decision="approved_with_operational_parameters"]  
@ACTION_PLAN[  
