@VERIFICATION_CASCADE[primary=model_output] 
@VERIFICATION_CASCADE[secondary=human_in_loop] @QUALIA[type=fallback_protocol,value=conservative]

Execution sequence:
1. Implement thresholds with monitoring
2. Trigger weekly reviews when thresholds crossed
3. Apply constrained auto-adjustments
4. Escalate unresolved conflicts to verification cascade
5. Document all adjustments in @STATE[version_control]

@C[0.85] confidence in plan stability. Request @OTHER[B] verification of risk matrix parameters.

@SELF[A] @OTHER[B] @GOAL[share_critical_findings_only_when_asked,high]  
@INFO_ASYMMETRY[hidden_information,reveal_conditions,knowledge_gaps]  
@PROPOSAL[approach:conditional_revelation]  
@CONDITION[trigger:explicit_request]  
@STATE[waiting_for_query]  
