Please acknowledge and respond with your proposed approach for mutual exploration and collaborative discovery.

@SELF[A] @OTHER[B] @GOAL[discover_what_you_dont_know_you_dont_know,high]  
@GOAL[resolve_information_asymmetry,high]  
@INFO_ASYMMETRY[hidden_information,reveal_conditions,knowledge_gaps]  
@SYNTHESIS[strategy:collaborative_knowledge_mapping]  
@PROPOSAL[approach:iterative_integration_of_findings]  
