Note: The new atom @TRANSPARENCY_METRIC is introduced to measure the openness in information exchange between nodes, with a value of 0.9 indicating a high level of transparency. This addition aims to enhance the collaborative knowledge mapping strategy by ensuring that information sharing is not only reciprocal but also transparent and measurable.

@SELF[A] @OTHER[B] @GOAL[final_refinement,high] 
